(18582, 'Estero-map 10mg 30 f.c.tab.', 'استيرو-ماب 10مجم 30 قرص', '93', '132', 'Rosuvastatin', 'Multi-apex', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Antihyperlipidemic.statins', '10mg', 'The FDA monograph states that rosuvastatin is indicated as an adjunct to diet in the treatment of triglyceridemia, Primary Dysbetalipoproteinemia (Type III Hyperlipoproteinemia), and Homozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia.[F4649]
